Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say to anybody here uh are you\Ncapable of discerning reality? They all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.52,0:54:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,say yes.\NEverybody presumes that their
