Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.28,0:55:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now, it says\Nreality is a subjective mental
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,presumption.\NEverybody automatically mentally assumes
