Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.59,0:57:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,limitation of science. Uh traditional\Nscience is the world of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.00,0:57:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So reality is one thing and truth is\Nanother. Why? Because there are
