Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.68,1:02:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hurt their feelings by\Ntelling them they're being sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.31,1:02:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The narcissistic generation is so exalts\Nthe inner ego
