Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.55,1:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're insulted, don't try and change\Nthe world. Try to transcend your ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.55,1:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The world in the universe, evolution, is\Nnot going to cater to your personal ego
